## Op vocabulary

| Op | Meaning |
|----|---------|
| `ingest` | A document was read and its facts extracted into one or more pages |
| `page-add` | A new wiki page was created |
| `page-update` | An existing wiki page was updated (content or frontmatter) |
| `decision-record` | A new decision page was added (ADR) |
| `merge` | Two near-duplicate pages were merged into one canonical page |
| `reconcile` | A checkpoint reconcile pass ran (reflect → capture → merge → refresh index) |
| `lint` | `brain_lint.py` was run; findings noted |

